sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户输入
    participant REPL as REPL
    participant QE as QueryEngine
    participant Q as query.ts
    participant API as Claude API
    participant T as Tool（任意工具）

    User->>REPL: 输入文本
    REPL->>QE: submitMessage()
    QE->>Q: query()
    Q->>API: 流式请求
    API-->>Q: tool_use block
    Q->>T: tool.call()
    T-->>Q: ToolResult
    Q->>API: tool_result 回填
    API-->>Q: 继续流式输出
    Q-->>QE: yield 事件流
    QE-->>REPL: 更新 UI
